{"tid":2073521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6.28 靜默遊行 佐敦至旺角","createTime":"2020-06-21T11:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T08:14:57.000Z","uid":205927,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4d211622cc56455524b63ffa0960a101837527c1","tid":2073521,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:35:46.000Z","msg":"628有遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快做文宣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72KCAhE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72KCAhE.jpg&h=0565ed73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.28 靜默遊行 3時出發  <br />\n<br />\n本次行動本著以下原則進行<br />\n<br />\n不集合❗️不口號❗️不逗留❗️<br />\n<br />\n由佐敦A,B出口沿彌敦道行人道直到旺角解散<br />\n<br />\n⚠️請使用行人道進行本次行動<br />\n<br />\n❗️如被狗隻打斷或任何突發行動請轉入內街沿內街自行繼續/解散<br />\n<br />\n完成路程後請原地airdrop7.1有關文宣及離開<br />\n<br />\n本次行動為一個人抗爭系列之一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附上一張 7.1文宣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSycpbh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSycpbh.jpg&h=2ddeccfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab4c24ac3dbad3b3c3dcd34c95b85619487c96c6","tid":2073521,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9179d58703fb7b9debfa40d0650d1c831fe638a","tid":2073521,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"source:.tg: @stuckwithyou"},{"pid":"6673dbb99182fe90cffcbd6fd5798c1ff39196f1","tid":2073521,"uid":155012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class